quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  37,103,"Kho boosi babili olwa belekhulila Nyasaye, mana namukonelia obweni."
  37,104,"Nikhumulanga mbu: “Ewe Ibrahim!"
  37,105,"Toto omalile okhukhola habwene khumaloro kalia. Toto endio nilwa khurunganga Abakholi bamalayi."
  37,106,"Toto kano ni amatemo kali habulafu.”"
  37,107,"Mana nikhumuhelesia eshisinzo shioluyali."
  37,108,"Mana nikhumuleshela ifuma indayi khubetsa inyuma."
  37,109,"Omulembe kube khu Ibrahim."
  37,110,"Endio nilwa khurunganga Abakholi bamalayi."
  37,111,"Toto ye ali Mubandu befu basuubila."
  37,112,"Ne nikhumuboolera koomwikhoyo, kokhwibulwa khwa Is’haaq, abe Omurumwa womubandu Abalayi."
  37,113,"Mana nikhumuhelesia tsikhabi ye nende Is’haaq. Ne mulwibulo lwabu, nibarulamwo Abandu abalayi nende balia bekholela amabii habulafu."
  37,114,"Ne toto khwakholela obulayi Musa nende Harun."
  37,115,"Nikhubahabina halala nende Abandu babu okhurulana nende obutinyu obukhongo."
  37,116,"Mana nikhubakhonya nibaba nibo abashili."
  37,117,"Ne nikhuhelesia babili abo Eshitabu shinoosinjia."
  37,118,"Mana nikhubalunjisia khunjila ingololofu."
  37,119,"Mana nikhubaleshela ifuma indayi khubalia betsa inyuma wabu."
  37,120,"Omulembe kube khu Musa nende Harun."
  37,121,"Toto endio nilwakhurunganga abalayi."
  37,122,"Toto babili abo bali Mubasumba befu Abasuubili."
  37,123,"Ne toto Elyas yali Mubarumwa."
  37,124,"Olwa yaboolela Abandu bebe mbu: “Shimuritsanga tawe?"
  37,125,"Mulaamanga Baal (eshimoosi shieidhahabu) ne mulekha omuloonji omulayi mwene?"
  37,126,"Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi nende wa bapapa benyu bakhale.”"